  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Threat to Members of Parliament'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Headquarters has directed the Criminal Investigation Department to initiate investigations against those who publish posts on social media threatening members of Parliament.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has also ordered an investigation into the allegations that some people are trying to interfere with the right to freely vote through social media by exerting influence or pressure on members of parliament to elect the next president.",
        "Accordingly, under the mandate of the Ministry of Public Security, the Police Headquarters has directed the Computer Crime Investigation Unit to enforce the law against those who create and publish such instructions on social media. (a)"
      ],
